snippet.title: WOH ‚Äì Ikka x Dino James x Badshah (Official Lyric Video) | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‚ÄòWoh.‚Äô The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is one of the very few records which portray a man‚Äôs emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah‚Äôs verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Portugal 2:0 Uruguay - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Bruno Fernandes scored a sensational goal from a cross-shot as Portugal edged Uruguay in a feisty Group H clash.

After a cagey first-half, Fernandes' curled home from distance & Cristiano Ronaldo appeared to have got something on that. But replays showed the ball went in directly without the skipper's intervention; thus rewarding the Manchester United midfielder his first #FIFAWorldCup goal.

Fernandes then converted his second from the spot after VAR intervened to award the 2016 European champions a penalty following a handball.

2-0 it ended on the night & the result Fernando Santos' side sealed their place in the Round of 16.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3627 - 28 Nov 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3627: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak's boss comes to his house and makes his way to Taarak's bedroom to see how he is doing. Everyone tries to stop him, but he succeeds in getting to Taarak this time. Taarak is surprisingly snoozing in his bed while feigning sleep. Everyone follows the boss, so when they discover him lying there, they are shocked. Taarak displays astonishment and acts to be innocent at seeing his boss at his house. The boss now requests that Taarak demonstrate his broken leg. The boss begins to mistrust Taarak as he rips away the blanket from which he had wrapped his leg with Anjali's dupatta. The boss also questions about the leg he was hurt as he had watched it on the video call. Will Taarak be able to use his alibi successfully? Watch the full episode to know more.

Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 670 - 28 Nov 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 670: Cheetah Ka Dhokha
--------------------------------------------
The Chingaari gang members believe Karishma Singh is leaking information about them. Karishma Singh enters Rangez Galli with a bullet in her leg, but the people there are still hesitant to trust her because she works for the police. She informs everyone that Maddam Sir reached the place and shot her because Cheetah had already told Haseena about the Chingaari Gang's scheme. In an effort to determine the truth, Binny purposefully presses and examines Karishma's injury. Watch the episode to know more.
 
Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 670, 28 Nov 2022
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy.

snippet.title: Part 2: I took the WRONG TRAIN in Germany | Rahul Dua StandUp Comedy 2022 | UnRehearsed UnScripted
snippet.description:
Oh Hello! India Tour 2022-23 ‚ÄúOne Last Time‚Äù; All Shows' tickets live now: https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/oh-hello-by-rahul-dua-india-tour/ET00343031

Shot on 23rd April 2022 at Jarhunderthalle, Frankfurt (Germany)

This show was performed 3 days after this actual incident. Completely unrehearsed, unscripted, on the spot storytelling happened during my first ever Oh Hello! International StandUp Tour in Apr-May 2022.
In this sequel to Part 1 (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BaeM22LFLfQ&t=151s), I talk about how I took the wrong train at Hamburg, language issues, German punctuality, my interaction with the co-passengers and the train master and my almost-missed Berlin Show. 
And all of this after I successfully proclaimed and convinced India that trains are better than airplanes. 
After this, train are better for sure, but Indian Trains are better than German Trains.
#rahuldua #standupcomedy #germany 
Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/therahuldua

snippet.description:

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 671 - 28 Nov 2022
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#Maddam Sir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama and comedy.

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam.
